ship. THe energon exposure is eminent in his arms, as they flicker blue. "I
only need to refuel" he replies to Autofires point. "Lets talk first order
of buisness my comerade. Where can we strike first, that us two robots
could take, hmmm" he asked questioningly, as he stood at the ship, not sure
where to put the energon.
